Application Name Overview
==============================================

Codetry is a platform where coders from all over the world can post their poetry written in any code they like.


Required Environment / Minimum Setup
----------------------------------------------

Ruby version 1.9.3
Rails version 3.2.13
Minimum setup required to run the app. This should be checked by dev:setup


